OL,3,CParty Political Broadcasts: a headache
OL,4,Cfor schedulers
OL,6,GThey are probably the least popular
OL,7,G"programmes" on TV. Party Political
OL,8,GBroadcasts probably serve little
OL,9,Gpurpose ` it is simply that the
OL,10,Galternatives are worse.
OL,12,FHow many undecided voters tune in and
OL,13,Fhave their minds swayed?
OL,15,FHow many opponents of a party tune in
OL,16,Fto find out what the other lot think?
OL,18,FAbout the only good thing which can be
OL,19,Fsaid for them is that they are better
OL,20,Fin principal than paid for political
OL,21,FTV advertising.
