OL,3,CParty Political Broadcasts: a headache
OL,4,Cfor schedulers
OL,6,FViewers in England are currently
OL,7,Fsuffering a nightly dose of them ahead
OL,8,Fof May's local elections. The switch
OL,9,Foff on BBC One at 6.55pm does no good
OL,10,Fto The One Show.
OL,12,FIn the UK, TV advertising by political
OL,13,Fparties is not allowed although they
OL,14,Fcan advertise in newspapers and online
OL,15,F` subject to various rules concerning
OL,16,Ftotal expenditure.
