OL,3,CParty Political Broadcasts: a headache
OL,4,Cfor schedulers
OL,6,FIf you have ever been in the USA
OL,7,Fduring an election campaign, you may
OL,8,Fhave had the misfortune to see
OL,9,Fpolitical TV advertising ` more often
OL,10,Fthan not throwing mud at opponents
OL,11,Frather than saying anything positive
OL,12,Fabout the candidate or party the
OL,13,Fadvert is supposedly promoting.
OL,15,FSo you can see why there is an
OL,16,Fargument that Party Political
OL,17,FBroadcasts are at least fairer in
OL,18,Fprinciple.
