OL,3,CParty Political Broadcasts: a headache
OL,4,Cfor schedulers
OL,6,FBut given the fact that so few people
OL,7,Fwould positively want to watch them,
OL,8,Fthey are something of a nightmare for
OL,9,Fschedulers.
OL,11,FIn the old days, there was a
OL,12,Fconvention that these broadcasts went
OL,13,Fout simultaneously on all three
OL,14,Fchannels ` usually at 9pm.
OL,16,FSince the early 80s though, they have
OL,17,Fbeen scheduled in a different way.
OL,19,FThe current arrangements go back about
OL,20,F20 years.
