OL,3,CParty Political Broadcasts: a headache
OL,4,Cfor schedulers
OL,6,FBBC One shows them at around 6.55pm `
OL,7,Feating into the durations of both the
OL,8,Fnational and regional news. ITV 1
OL,9,Fshows them at 6.25pm at the expense of
OL,10,Fthe regional news.
OL,12,FBBC Two stopped screening them about 5
OL,13,Fyears ago ` presumably when BBC
OL,14,FScotland lost the ability to opt on
OL,15,FBBC Two, as care is taken to make sure
OL,16,Fbroadcasts are relevant to the
OL,17,Fappropriate nation. In Scotland there
OL,18,Fwould be a clear problem if the three
OL,19,FUK parties had broadcasts on BBC Two
OL,20,Fbut not the SNP.
