OL,3,CParty Political Broadcasts: a headache
OL,4,Cfor schedulers
OL,6,FChannel 4 and Channel 5 do not screen
OL,7,FPPBs except during General Election
OL,8,Fcampaigns.
OL,10,FThe effect of the current scheduling
OL,11,Farrangements on the two big channels
OL,12,Fis painful.
OL,14,FIt basically cuts the time available
OL,15,Ffor news and cuts the audience for The
OL,16,FOne Show and the ITV Evening News.
OL,18,FViewers do vote ` with their remotes.
OL,20,FBut if you accept that PPBs are less
OL,21,Fundesirable than the alternatives,
OL,22,Fwhere else could they go?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/9
