OL,3,CParty Political Broadcasts: a headache
OL,4,Cfor schedulers
OL,6,F5.55pm or 10.40pm would mean they were
OL,7,Fshown out of peak ` less disruptive
OL,8,Fbut also less viewed.
OL,10,FShowing then simultaneously at say
OL,11,F10pm on the two big channels and
OL,12,Fdelaying the news would simply drive
OL,13,Fviewers elsewhere.
OL,15,FBBC One could conceivably tweak things
OL,16,Fso that PPBs came between The One Show
OL,17,Fand EastEnders but again there are
OL,18,Fproblems.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G7/9
