OL,3,CParty Political Broadcasts: a headache
OL,4,Cfor schedulers
OL,6,FA shorter duration for The One Show
OL,7,Ffor a broadcast not being shown in a
OL,8,Fparticular nation would leave a very
OL,9,Flong time to collapse into trails.
OL,11,FITV 1 would face similar issues if it
OL,12,Fproposed running PPBs at about 7.25pm
OL,13,Fat the expense of a few minutes of
OL,14,Fnational news.
OL,16,FIt is tempting to come to the
OL,17,Fconclusion that PPBs should just be
OL,18,Fabandoned. Personally I wish this
OL,19,Fcould happen.
