OL,3,CParty Political Broadcasts: a headache
OL,4,Cfor schedulers
OL,6,FBut good luck to broadcasters trying
OL,7,Fto persuade politicians who value
OL,8,Fhaving a bit of airtime free from
OL,9,Fjournalists asking them questions and
OL,10,Fholding them to account.
OL,12,FOr could political TV advertising with
OL,13,Ftight rules and restrictions ` e.g.,
OL,14,Flimited expenditure, no negative
OL,15,Fcampaigning ` be allowed?
OL,17,FThere are no easy answers.
OL,19,FThe undesirability of PPBs does not
OL,20,Fmake the alternatives less unpalatable.
